snippet `(b|p|v)mata([1-9])` "bmatrix" iiAm
\\begin{``rv = m[1]``matrix}``
	let len = m[2];
	let results = "";
	for (var i=0; i<len; i++){
		results += "$1 &".repeat(len-1) + " $1 \\\\\\\\";
	}
	rv = results;
``\\end{``rv = m[1]``matrix}$0
endsnippet

